quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,(Ndifunga) ngezo ngelosi zikreliswe ngokwemigca
  37,2,Nangezo ziqhuba amafu
  37,3,Nangezo zicengceleza umyalezo (wesiTyhilelo)
  37,4,Inene uThixo wakho Mnye
  37,5,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba noko kungaphakathi kwawo, EkwayiNkosi yeeMpumalanga"
  37,6,Inene Thina Silihombisile izulu elikufutshane ngeenkwenkwezi zokuhombisa
  37,7,Ezikwalukhuselo ngokuchasene naye nawuphi na uShaytân ongumvukeli
  37,8,Ukuze (bangachwechwi) baye kuphulaphula intlanganiso ebekekileyo (yeengelosi) yaye (aba Sathana) baxulutywa (ngamadangatya omlilo) macala onke (abazama ukuvela ngakuwo)
  37,9,Bagxothwe; yaye abakufumanayo kukohlwaywa rhoqo
  37,10,"Ngaphandle kwabo baxhwila (amazwi athile) ngobusela, kodwa nabo bayaleqwa ngezikhuni ezivuthayo, (ezikhanya) ngokugqobhozelayo"
  37,11,"Khawubabuze (Muhammad) okukuba ingaba ngabo na abayeyona ndalo iqinileyo okanye yenye na (indalo enjengamazulu nomhlaba neentaba) eSazidalayo? Inene, bona Sabadala ngodongwe oluncangathi"
  37,12,Ewe kakade (wena Muhammad) uye wamangaliseka (yindelelo yabo) xa bebekugculela (wena ne’Kur’ân)
  37,13,Naxa bekhunjuzwa (ngoAllâh) abahoyi
  37,14,Naxa bebona umqondiso bayawugculela
  37,15,"Bade bathi: “Asinto yimbi le ngaphandle kokuba ngumlingo ocacileyo"
  37,16,Ingaba xa sifile sele siluthuli namathambo siza kuphinda sivuswe kwakhona
  37,17,Ndawonye noobawo bethu bamandulo?”
  37,18,"Yithi wena (Muhammad): “Ewe, yaye niya kuhlaziswa.”"
  37,19,"Iya kuba sisikhalo esinye (seXilongo), yabonani! Baya kuthi ndlaa (amehlo besoyika)"
  37,20,"Baya\tkuthi:\t“Yeha\tkuthi!\tLe\tyiyo\t(ngenene)\tiMini yembuyekezo!”"
  37,21,"(Kuya kuthiwa kubo): “Yiyo le ke iMini yoMgwebo enanidla ngokuyiphika.”"
  37,22,"(Kuya kuthiwa kwiingelosi): “Qokelelani ndaweninye bonke abo benza ubugwenxa, bedibene noogxa babo (ooSathana abangamademon) nezo nto2 babedla ngokuzikhonza"
  37,23,"Endaweni ka-Allâh, nibakhokelele endleleni eya edangatyeni loMlilo (isiHogo)"
  37,24,"Kodwa khanibamise, kuba inene bona kufuneka bebuziwe"
  37,25,"Yintoni ngani, yini na ebangela ukuba ningancedisani (njengoko nanincedisana emhlabeni)"
  37,26,"Nakanye, bona baya kusuka bazinikezele"
  37,27,"Ke kaloku baya kujika bajongane , babuzane"
  37,28,"Baya kuthi: “Nini (booSathana) ababedla ngokuza kuthi nivela ngasekunene kwethu (nisilahlekise ngokusenzela ntle indlela eya ekwenzeni ubutshinga)”"
  37,29,"Baya kuphendula ke bona: “Unotshe! Nini ngokwenu eningazanga nikholwe"
  37,30,"Ngapha koko thina sasingenagunya phezu kwenu. Nakanye, nina nasuka naba ngabagabadeli"
  37,31,"“Ngoku ke iLizwi leNkosi yethu liyathetheleka ngokuchasene nathi, mayela nokuba singcamle (isohlwayo)"
  37,32,"Ke\tngoko\tsanikhokelela\tekulahlekeni\tkuba\tnathi sasilahlekile.”"
  37,33,Inene ngaloo Mini baya kwabelana ngesohlwayo
  37,34,"Ngokwenene, leyo yindlela esiqubisana ngayo nabenzi bobubi"
  37,35,"Ke kaloku, xa kusithiwa kubo: “Akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle koAllâh,” bona bayazikhukhumalisa, (baphikise)"
  37,36,"Kananjalo bathi: “Siza kushiya oothixo bethu ngenxa yembongi ephambeneyo na"
  37,37,Nakanye! Yena (uMuhammad) ufike nenyaniso (i-Islam ne’Kur’ân) yaye yena uyabangqina abaThunywa (abangaphambili kunaye)
  37,38,Inene nina (bahedenindini) niza kusingcamla isohlwayo esibuhlungu
  37,39,Kananjalo aniyi kubuyekezwa nganto ngaphandle koko nanidla ngokukwenza
  37,40,Ngaphandle kwezicaka ezinyanisekileyo zika-Allâh
  37,41,Kwabo banjalo kuya kubakho umsindleko owaziwayo
  37,42,Iziqhamo yaye baya kuhlonipheka
  37,43,EMiyezweni yolonwabo
  37,44,Bejongene (behleli zava) ezitroneni
  37,45,Emacaleni abo kuya kuba kugqithiswa indebe yewayini elungileyo (ehlambulukileyo)
  37,46,Emhlophe nenencasa kwabayiselayo
  37,47,"Abayi kuva buhlungu apho nabubi, bengayi kuva kunxila nakuyotywa (apho)"
  37,48,"Kanti\temacaleni\tkwabo\tkuya\tkubakho\tabasetyhini, ababajezula ngamehlo abo amahle"
  37,49,"(Ababuthathaka,\tbenyulu)\tngokungengathi\tngamaqanda anonotshelweyo"
  37,50,Ke kaloku baya kujongana babuzane
  37,51,"Isithethi phakathi kwabo siya kuthi: “Ndandinomhlobo (ehlabathini)"
  37,52,"Owayedla ngokuthi (kum): “Ingaba wena ungomnye wabo bakholwayo (kuvuko lwasemva kokufa na)?”"
  37,53,"Esithi (kananjalo): “Ingaba xa sele sifile, siluthuli namathambo, siza kuvuswa ngenene samkeliswe umvuzo okanye isohlwayo kusini na?”"
  37,54,"Kwathiwa kuye: “Ungakhe ujonge phantsi na?”"
  37,55,Wajonga ke phantsi waza wambona (umhlobo lowo wakhe) esazulwini soMlilo
  37,56,"Wathi kuye: “Ndifunga ngoAllâh, inene wena waphantsela ukunditshabalalisa"
  37,57,"Ukuba ngaba kwakungekho ngenxa yoBabalo lweNkosi yam, inene le, ngendandibe ngomnye wabo batyhalelwa (eMlilweni).”"
  37,58,"(Ke kaloku abemi basePaladesi baya kuthi): Ingaba asizi kuphinda sife kwakhona na"
  37,59,"Ngaphandle kokufa kwethu okokuqala, kananjalo ingaba asizi kohlwaywa na (emva kokungena kwethu eMyezweni?)”"
  37,60,"Inene, le yimpumelelo enkulu"
  37,61,Ngenxa yokunjengoku abasebenzi (bokulungileyo) mabasebenze
  37,62,Ingaba yiPaladesi na elungileyo okanye ngumthi weZa’kkum (umthi ombi osesihogweni)
  37,63,Inene wona siwenze waba yintshutshiso kubenzi bobubi
  37,64,Inene wona ngumthi ohluma ngaphantsi koMlilo wesiHogo
  37,65,Amagaqa eziqhamo zawo anjengeentloko zamashayâtîn (amademon)
  37,66,Inene baza kutyiswa (ezo ziqhamo) bazalise izisu zabo ngazo
  37,67,"Baze phezu koko banikwe amanzi abilayo, ukuba basele khona ukuze ibe ngumxube (wamanzi eZa’kkum ngaphakathi eziswini zabo)"
  37,68,Kuze emva koko inene ibe kukubuyiselwa kwabo eMlilweni wesiHogo odwanguzayo
  37,69,Inene bona bafumana ookhokho babo besendleleni egwenxa
  37,70,Ngoko ke nabo balandela ezinyaweni zabo
  37,71,Yaye inene uninzi lwabantu bakudala ababandulelayo babelahlekile
  37,72,"Kananjalo\tThina\tSasithumela\tabalumkisi\t(abaprofeti) phakathi kwabo"
  37,73,Khangelakeukubasabanjaninaisiphelosabobabelunyukisiwe (abamamela)
  37,74,Ngaphandle kwezicaka ezikhethiweyo zika-Allâh
  37,75,"Kananjalo uNûh wathandaza kuThi, yaye Thina Singabona balungileyo ukuphendula (imithandazo)"
  37,76,Ke kaloku Samsindisa yena nosapho lwakhe embandezelweni enkulu (yokurhaxwa ngamanzi)
  37,77,Kanti nenzala yakhe yona Sayenza ukuba ibe ngabasindileyo
  37,78,Saza Samshiyela (inkumbulo elungileyo) kwizizukulwana ezalandelayo emva koko
  37,79,Uxolo malube phezu koNûh emaphakadeni
  37,80,Siwavuza ngolo hlobo ke amalungisa
  37,81,"Inene, yena uNûh wayengomnye wabo babekholiwe kuThi"
  37,82,Kananjalo Sabatshonisa emanzini abanye
  37,83,Ke kaloku phakathi kwabo balandela indlela yakhe (uNûh) yaba nguIbrâhîm
  37,84,Wathi akuza eNkosini yakhe ngentliziyo ehlambulukileyo
  37,85,"Yabona; wathi kuyise nakubantu bakubo: “Yintoni na le niyinqulayo (apha)?”"
  37,86,“Ingaba ngoothixo bobuxoki na aba nifuna bona nina
  37,87,Kanti nicinga ntoni ngeNkosi uMlondolozi wamazwe?”
  37,88,Waza wakrwaqula ezinkwenkwezini
  37,89,"Wathi: “Inene mna ndigula (sisibetho3)”"
  37,90,Bahamba ke bamshiya (besoyika ukusulelwa sisifo eso)
  37,91,"Wabuyela yena kwizithixo zabo wathi: “Aniyi kutya na (kwiminikelo yamadini abekwe phambi kwenu?”)"
  37,92,Kuqhubeka ntoni kanye ngani ningathethi nje
  37,93,Waphethukela kuzo wazibetha ngesandla sakhe sokunene
  37,94,"Baza bona abakhonzi bezithixo, beza kuye ngokungxama"
  37,95,"Wathi yena (kubo): “Ingaba nina ninqula oko nikwenze (ngezandla zenu) na?”"
  37,96,Lo gama uAllâh Edale nina kunye noko nikwenzayo (kuzizithixo)!”
  37,97,"Bathi bona: “Makheleni isakhiwo (esiliziko uIbrâhîm), nize nimphose edangatyeni lomlilo!”"
  37,98,Baqulunqa iyelenqe elo ke kodwa Sasuka Sabenza bangabona bangaphantsi
  37,99,"Ke kaloku wathi yena (emva kokuba ehlanguliwe emlilweni): “InenemnandiyakuyaeNkosiniyam,Yiyo Eyakundikhokela"
  37,100,Nkosi yam ndiphe (inzala) eya kuba phakathi kwamalungisa.”
  37,101,Samnika iindaba ezilungileyo zomntwana oyinkwenkwe enomonde
  37,102,"Wathi unyana (wakhe lowo) esakuba emdala ngokwaneleyo ukuba ahambe naye, wathi kuye: “O nyana wam! Ndibone ephupheni ndixhela wena (njengedini lomnikelo kuAllah). Bona wena ke ukuba ucinga ntoni na!” Wathi yena: “O tata! Yenza oko ukuyalelweyo, ukuba uAllâh Uyavuma uya kundifumana ndingonyamezelayo.”"
  37,103,"Bathi ke besakuba bezinikele bobabini (phantsi kwentando ka-Allâh),Waba sele emlalise phantsi emqubudise ngebunzi lakhe (elungiselela ukumnqumla umqala)"
  37,104,"Samkhwaza: “Hini na Ibrâhîm"
  37,105,"Ulizalisekisile\tiphupha!”\tSiwavuza\tkanjalo\tke\tThina amalungisa"
  37,106,Olo yayilucikido lokwenene
  37,107,Samkhulula ngedini elikhulu (inkunzi yegusha)
  37,108,"Kananjalo\tyena\tsamshiyela\t(inkumbulo\telungileyo) kwizizukulwana ezisezayo"
  37,109,Uxolo malube kuIbrâhîm
  37,110,Siwavuza ngolo hlobo ke amalungisa
  37,111,Inene yena wayengomnye wabakhonzi beThu ababekholiwe
  37,112,Samnika iindaba ezivuyisayo zikaIs-hâ’k (uIsake)
  37,113,"Samsikelela yena noIs-hâ’k kodwa kwinzala yabo kukho abo benza okulungileyo, nabo bazona (imiphefumlo yabo) ngokuselubala"
  37,114,Kananjalo Senzela ubabalo uMûsâ noHârûn (uAron)
  37,115,Sabasindisa bona nabantu bakubo kwinkxwaleko enkulu
  37,116,"Sabanceda, khona ukuze babe noloyiso"
  37,117,Ke kaloku Sabanika isiBhalo esicacileyo
  37,118,Sabakhokelela eNdleleni ethe Tye
  37,119,"Sabashiyela\t(inkumbulo\telungileyo)\tkwizizukulwana ezisezayo"
  37,120,“Uxolo malube kuMûsâ noHârûn!”
  37,121,Sibavuza kanjalo ke Thina abenzi bokulungileyo
  37,122,Inene bona (uMûsâ noHârûn) babezizicaka zeThu ezibini ezikholwayo
  37,123,Kananjalo uIlyâs (uEliya) yayingomnye wabaThunywa
  37,124,"Xa wathi kubantu bakubo: “Aniyi kumoyika na uAllâh?”"
  37,125,Ingaba niza kubiza kuBhali na niyeke Oyena Mdali Wokwenene
  37,126,"uAllâh OyiNkosi yenu, OyiNkosi yooyihlo’mkhulu?”"
  37,127,"Kodwa basuka bamphikisa yena (uIlyâs)4, ngoko ke baza kuziswa ngaphambili (esohlwayweni)"
  37,128,Ngaphandle kwezicaka ezikhethiweyo zika-Allâh
  37,129,Yena Samshiyela (inkumbulo elungileyo) kwizizukulwana ezisezayo
  37,130,“Uxolo malube kuIlyâsiîn!”
  37,131,Sibavuza kanjalo keThina abenzi bokulungileyo
  37,132,Inene yena wayengomnye wezicaka zeThu ezikholiweyo
  37,133,Kanti noLût yayingomnye wabaThunywa
  37,134,Xa Samsindisayo yena nosapho lwakhe lonke
  37,135,Ngaphandle kwexhegokazi (umkakhe) elaba ngomnye wabo bashiyeka ngemva
  37,136,Sabatshabalalisa bonke abanye (bezixeko ezo iSodom neGomora)
  37,137,Inene nina nigqitha ngakubo (abo bafela apho) ekuseni
  37,138,Nasebusuku; ingaba aniyi kucingisisa na
  37,139,Kanti noYûnus wayengomnye wabaThunywa
  37,140,Xa wabalekela kwinqanawa eyayinomthwalo
  37,141,"Wavuma ke ukwenza amaqashiso, waza waba ngomnye wabo balahlekelwayo"
  37,142,Ke kaloku intlanzi enkulu yamginya njengoko wayenze isenzo esigxekekileyo
  37,143,Ukuba ngaba wayengazanga abe ngomnye wabo bazukisa uAllâh
  37,144,Inene yena wayeza kuhlala esiswini sentlanzi de kube yimini yoVuko
  37,145,Kodwa Samphosela elunxwemeni egula enjalo
  37,146,Ke kaloku Sahlumisa umthi womhlavuthwa phezu kwakhe (ngentla kwakhe)
  37,147,Kananjalo Samthumela kubantu abangamawaka aliwaka nangaphezulu kunoko
  37,148,Bakholwa ke; Saza Sabanika ulonwabo lokwethutyana
  37,149,"Ngoku ke khawubabuze (Muhammad): “Ingaba ziintombi5 (zodwa) na Enazo iNkosi yakho baze bona babe noonyana na?”"
  37,150,"Okanye\tmhlawumbi\t(bathi)\tSadala\tiingelosi\tzaba ngabasetyhini lo gama babebukele bona kusini na"
  37,151,Inene kungobuxoki babo le nto abahedeni besithi
  37,152,"“UAllâh Uzele”, bona ngamaxoki okwenene"
  37,153,Ingaba Yena Uzikhethele iintombi kusini na endaweni yoonyana
  37,154,Yintoni na ngani? Nigweba njani kanye
  37,155,Kanti aniqaphelisisi na
  37,156,Okanye mhlawumbi ninegunya elicacileyo nina
  37,157,Yizani nencwadi yenu kaloku ukuba ninenyaniso
  37,158,"Kananjalo baye baqamba ukuhlobana phakathi kwaKhe neeJinni, kodwa zona iiJinni ziyazi (kakuhle) okokuba ziza kuma (phambi kwaKhe ziphendule ngezenzo zazo)"
  37,159,"Uzuko\tlonke\tmalube\tkuAllâh!\t(Okude\tlee)\tkoko bakwayamanisa naYe"
  37,160,"Ngaphandle kwezicaka zika-Allâh, Awazikhethayo"
  37,161,Ngoko ke inene nina bahedeni ndawonye nabo nibanqulayo (izinyanya)
  37,162,Abangekhe balahlekise (nabani na kumakholwa) bamwexule kuYe (uAllâh)
  37,163,Ngaphandle kwalowo umiselwe ukuba atshe esiHogweni
  37,164,Yaye akukho namnye kuthi (ingelosi) koko unendawo yakhe eyaziwayo
  37,165,Kananjalo thina (zingelosi) sima ngokwemigca (sithandaze phambi koAllah)
  37,166,Yaye futhi thina (zingelosi) inene singabo bazukisa uAllâh
  37,167,Kananjalo bona (abahedeni) babedla ngokuthi
  37,168,“Ukuba sasibe naye umlumkisi njengabantu bamandulo
  37,169,Sasiya kuba zizicaka zika-Allâh ezikhethiweyo
  37,170,Kodwa (ngoku i’Kur’ân ifikile) abakholwa kuyo. Ngoko ke baza kwazi
  37,171,"Inene lona ilizwi leThu sele liphumile, kwamandulo mayela neziCaka zeThu abaProfeti"
  37,172,Elokuba ngabo ngokwenene abaza kuba noloyiso
  37,173,Kwanokuba imikhosi yeThu yiyo eza kuba yeyoyisayo
  37,174,Shenxa ke kubo (wena Muhammad) okwethutyana
  37,175,Ubajonge yaye baza kusibona (isohlwayo)
  37,176,Ingaba bafuna ukuba isohlwayo sikhawuleziswe
  37,177,"Ke kaloku ukuhla kwaso singena emizini yabo, iya kuba mbi intsasa (yaloo mini) kwabo babelunyukisiwe"
  37,178,Ngoko ke (wena Muhammad) bashiye okwethutyana
  37,179,"Ubajonge, yaye baza kubona (isohlwayo)"
  37,180,"Uzuko lonke malube seNkosini yakho, iNkosi yobunganga namandla (Ekude lee) koko bakwayamanisa naYo"
  37,181,Uxolo malube kubaThunywa
  37,182,"Neendumiso zonke mazibe kuAllâh, iNkosi uMlondolozi wamazwe"